            assistant, camera assistant, freelance photographer, and studio
            photographer. Presently, Matt is a full-time assistant editor for
            the marketing campaigns of major streaming services such as Amazon
            Prime and Paramount+. For this reason, Rent-A-Booth LA is limited to
            weekend availability.
          </p>
